|---|---|
| **E-1 (staging Gap-1/Gap-3 CLOSED ÔÇö E9 carry retired)** | Both staging compose files exist on origin/main: `docker-compose.staging.yml` (111 lines, local-dev CHARLIE bot-path) **and** `docker-compose.staging-vps.yml` (19 KB, the deployed always-on VPS stack ÔÇö project `mira-staging`, offset ports `stg-mira-hub:4101`/pipeline:4099/web:4200, pointed at staging Neon `ep-polished-hall`, **not** prod). Staging bot is `@Mira_stagong_bot` (token `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN_STG`), never `@FactoryLM_Diagnose`. `docs/environments.md` marks Gap-1 + Gap-3 closed. Ôçĺ root `CLAUDE.md` Environments table is **stale** (still tags both `*(TODO)*`) Ôćĺ staged `patches/2026-06-19-E10-claude-md-staging-todo-stale.patch` (apply-check CLEAN vs origin/main). |
